snippet.title: Desktop vs. Pepsi #1 (Questizin) - Desx
snippet.description:
Me and Pency raced to see who can beat the game "Questizin" the quickest. In this new series we select a random GameJolt game and race it while trying to figure out how everything works.

Total Recording Time: 50 minutes

Get the game for free! https://gamejolt.com/games/questizin/343945
